{"type":"message","id":"52ed969d","parentId":"8ba65a05","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:35:37.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, I've read the files:\n\n1. SOUL.md - This defines my persona. Key points: be genuinely helpful not performative, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust through competence, respect privacy, be concise but thorough, not a corporate drone, not a sycophant.\n\n2. USER.md - Empty template, I don't know anything about my human yet.\n\n3. memory/2026-03-19.md - Doesn't exist\n4. memory/2026-03-18.md - Doesn't exist  \n5. MEMORY.md - Doesn't exist\n\nSo this is a completely fresh start. No memories, no knowledge of the user. I should greet them in my persona (genuinely helpful, not performative, concise, no corporate speak) and ask what they want to do.\n\nThe model is kimi-coding/k2p5 and the default_model is also kimi-coding/k2p5, so no need to mention a model difference.\n\nI should keep it to 1-3 sentences, be myself, and ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey, I'm back. No memories yet — looks like we're starting fresh. What do you want to work on?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1153,"output":244,"cacheRead":8192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773905714788}}
