{"type":"message","id":"ba46d658","parentId":"02a498b1","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:37:00.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问我有哪些技能（skills）。让我查看一下可用技能列表，我之前已经从系统提示中获得了这些信息。\n\n根据系统提示中的 `<available_skills>` 部分，我有以下技能：\n\n1. **feishu-doc** - 飞书文档读写操作\n2. **feishu-drive** - 飞书云存储文件管理\n3. **feishu-perm** - 飞书权限管理\n4. **feishu-wiki** - 飞书知识库导航\n5. **clawhub** - ClawHub CLI 用于搜索、安装、更新和发布 agent skills\n6. **coding-agent** - 委托编码任务给 Codex、Claude Code 或 Pi agents\n7. **healthcheck** - 主机安全加固和风险配置\n8. **node-connect** - 诊断 OpenClaw 节点连接和配对失败\n9. **skill-creator** - 创建、编辑、改进或审核 AgentSkills\n10. **weather** - 获取当前天气和预报\n11. **HTTP** - 正确使用 HTTP\n\n我应该用简洁的方式列出这些技能，按照 SOUL.md 的要求，跳过客套话，直接提供有用的信息。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我有以下技能可用：\n\n**飞书相关**\n- `feishu-doc` — 文档读写\n- `feishu-drive` — 云盘文件管理\n- `feishu-perm` — 权限管理\n- `feishu-wiki` — 知识库导航\n\n**开发工具**\n- `coding-agent` — 委托编码任务（Codex/Claude Code/Pi）\n- `skill-creator` — 创建/改进 agent skills\n- `clawhub` — 从 clawhub.com 搜索/安装/发布技能\n\n**系统与网络**\n- `healthcheck` — 安全审计与加固\n- `node-connect` — 诊断节点连接问题\n\n**其他**\n- `weather` — 天气查询\n- `HTTP` — HTTP 请求\n\n需要我用哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":349,"output":430,"cacheRead":9472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773905802101}}
