{"type":"message","id":"155c7483","parentId":"8a7eb944","timestamp":"2026-03-19T07:43:08.757Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to send an image from a local file path to Feishu. I need to use the `message` tool with `action: \"send\"` and provide the file path.\n\nLooking at the tool definition for `message`, I can see:\n- `action: \"send\"` is required\n- `filePath` or `path` can be used for the file location\n- I should not include `message` since I'm sending a file (or can include a caption)\n\nLet me send the image to the current Feishu conversation. The user is chatting via Feishu (channel: feishu), so I don't need to specify a target - it will go to the current conversation.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_kZFtwxul8xVc8fgwMls4bQIv","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","filePath":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/media/inbound/dde0d7ca-883a-42e5-8e1d-ccee82ed8c2f.jpg"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":596,"output":203,"cacheRead":9728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773906179050}}
