{"type":"message","id":"59991b4c","parentId":"2921a752","timestamp":"2026-03-19T08:57:54.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来我直接访问配置文件也受到沙箱限制。让我建议用户手动检查配置文件，或者我可以建议他们使用 `openclaw config` 命令来查看/修改配置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"由于沙箱限制，我无法直接读取你的 OpenClaw 配置文件。请在你的服务器上执行以下操作：\n\n## 检查当前配置\n\n```bash\n# 查看配置文件路径和内容\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.yaml 2>/dev/null || cat ~/.openclaw/config.json 2>/dev/null\n\n# 或使用 OpenClaw CLI\nopenclaw config get tools\n```\n\n## 启用 exec 工具\n\n编辑配置文件（`~/.openclaw/config.yaml`），添加：\n\n```yaml\ntools:\n  exec:\n    enabled: true\n```\n\n## 重启服务\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n**完成后**，验证 exec 是否可用：\n```bash\nopenclaw exec -- echo \"test\"\n```\n\n如果显示 `test`，说明代码执行已启用。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":594,"output":205,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19999,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773910666074}}
