{"type":"message","id":"ccd81681","parentId":"7e7c5c8f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:16:48.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户指出配置文件位置是 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，而不是我之前说的 `config.yaml`。用户说我的信息不是最新的。\n\n我需要承认错误，并更新信息。让我提供正确的配置指导。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，感谢纠正！配置文件是 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`。\n\n## 正确的配置步骤\n\n### 1. 检查当前配置\n\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n### 2. 启用 exec 工具\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加或修改 `tools` 部分：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"exec\": {\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 4. 验证\n\n```bash\nopenclaw exec -- echo \"test\"\n```\n\n---\n\n还有其他我需要更新的信息吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":19854,"output":199,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20309,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773911797141}}
