{"type":"message","id":"34b63491","parentId":"702619a8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:22:38.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能不在 workspace 里，可能在系统路径。让我尝试用系统路径读取，或者基于我了解的 clawhub 知识来回答。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"clawhub skill 的文件不在 workspace 中。根据 clawhub 的用法，安装技能的命令是：\n\n```bash\nclawhub install agent-reach\n```\n\n或者指定版本：\n```bash\nclawhub install agent-reach@latest\n```\n\n如果你想查看更多信息：\n```bash\nclawhub search agent-reach    # 搜索技能\nclawhub info agent-reach      # 查看技能详情\nclawhub list                  # 查看已安装技能\n```\n\n安装后可能需要重启 OpenClaw Gateway 来加载新技能：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n要我尝试用 clawhub skill 帮你安装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":317,"output":166,"cacheRead":24576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773912152870}}
