{"type":"message","id":"5a4372a0","parentId":"2ddfe85b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:26:15.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说他在 `~/.openclaw/skills` 中安装了一些技能，但我找不到。让我检查一下：\n\n1. 用户路径可能有拼写错误 - 他说 `skils`（少了一个 l），应该是 `skills`\n2. 也可能是正确的 `skills` 路径\n\n我应该检查一下 workspace 的 skills 目录，以及用户提到的路径。但由于沙箱限制，我可能无法访问 `~/.openclaw/skills`。\n\n让我先检查 workspace 中的 skills 目录。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下 workspace 中的 skills："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_E1GtIwq4dBkEsqLZUKOJpXBw","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant/skills/aliyun-image/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":508,"output":147,"cacheRead":25600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773912369951}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6b0653f","parentId":"5a4372a0","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:26:15.632Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_E1GtIwq4dBkEsqLZUKOJpXBw","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Aliyun Image Generation\n\nGenerate images using Alibaba Cloud DashScope (Qwen Image 2.0) API.\n\n## Usage\n\n```json\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"A cat wearing a hat\",\n  \"n\": 1,\n  \"negative_prompt\": \"\",\n  \"watermark\": false\n}\n```\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `prompt` (string, required): The text description of the image to generate\n- `n` (number, optional): Number of images to generate (default: 1)\n- `negative_prompt` (string, optional): Things to avoid in the image\n- `watermark` (boolean, optional): Whether to add watermark (default: false)\n- `reference_images` (array, optional): URLs of reference images to use\n\n## Example\n\n```json\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"图1中的女生穿着图2中的黑色裙子按图3的姿势坐下\",\n  \"reference_images\": [\n    \"https://example.com/image1.png\",\n    \"https://example.com/image2.png\",\n    \"https://example.com/image3.png\"\n  ],\n  \"n\": 2\n}\n```\n\n## API Reference\n\n- Endpoint: `https://dashscope-intl.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/multimodal-generation/generation`\n- Model: `qwen-image-2.0`\n- Documentation: https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/en/model-studio/developer-reference/qwen-image-2.0\n\n## Configuration\n\nSet your API key in `config.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"api_key\": \"your-dashscope-api-key\"\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773912375631}}
{"type":"message","id":"88d4a305","parentId":"d6b0653f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:26:24.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了 workspace 中的 aliyun-image skill。用户说他在 `~/.openclaw/skills` 安装了一些技能但找不到。\n\n有几个可能的原因：\n1. 路径问题 - 用户可能拼写错误（`skils` vs `skills`）\n2. 沙箱限制 - 我无法访问 workspace 外部的路径\n3. OpenClaw 可能需要重启来加载新安装的技能\n\n我应该询问用户具体安装了哪些技能，以及确认路径是否正确。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你提到路径是 `~/.openclaw/skils`（注意拼写：少了一个 **l**），正确路径应该是 `~/.openclaw/skills`。\n\n另外，我无法访问 workspace 外部的文件（沙箱限制），所以只能看到：\n- workspace 内的 `skills/` 目录\n- 系统预装的技能\n\n**可能的原因：**\n\n1. **拼写错误** — 确认是 `skills` 不是 `skils`\n2. **需要重启 Gateway** — 安装后需要重启才能加载新技能：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n3. **路径问题** — OpenClaw 可能从不同的路径加载 skills\n\n**你安装了哪些具体的技能？** 我可以帮你检查是否正确加载。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":745,"output":258,"cacheRead":25856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773912375633}}
