{"type":"message","id":"c0ff13c2","parentId":"4d9d61b5","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:05:42.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问如何配置才能让我使用 exec 工具。我需要告诉用户如何在 openclaw.json 中启用 exec 工具。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中，找到或添加 `tools` 配置：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"kimi-coding/k2p5\"\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"kimi-coding/k2p5\": { \n          \"alias\": \"Kimi K2.5\" \n        }\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"sandbox\": {\n        \"mode\": \"off\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"exec\": {\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n然后重启 Gateway：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**或者**如果已有 `tools` 部分，直接添加 `exec`：\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"exec\": { \"enabled\": true }\n}\n```\n\n重启后我就能执行命令了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":424,"output":236,"cacheRead":28928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29588,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773925535602}}
